%% Quote-to-cash lifecycle. See 04-domain-model.md, 09-data-architecture.md
sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Customer
  participant Q as /quote wizard
  participant API as API + tenant ctx
  participant AI as photoEstimate (L0)
  participant B as Booking/Job
  participant S as Stripe Connect
  participant L as LedgerEntry
  C->>Q: request estimate (photos)
  Q->>AI: photo -> load size + price range
  Q->>API: submit -> LeadCreated
  API->>B: BookingCreated (customerId)
  API->>S: Checkout Session (deposit)
  C->>S: pay deposit
  S-->>API: webhook DepositPaid (idempotent by session id)
  API->>L: LedgerEntry(revenue, deposit)
  Note over B: job runs (see job-lifecycle)
  API->>API: InvoiceIssued (balance)
  C->>S: pay balance
  S-->>API: PaymentReceived
  API->>L: LedgerEntry(revenue, balance)
  API->>L: LedgerEntry(payout to crew, expense)
  L-->>API: P&L / profitability read-model
